    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This powerplant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to produce a broad, linear powerband. The 6-speed Getrag 420G manual transmission provides precise shift gates, delivering power to the rear wheels through a functional M-Variable differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with refreshed bushings. While the aesthetic reflects its driven history, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive, providing an authentic analog performance experience.",
